data.description: PRICED TO SELL...PLUS 5K IN BUYER CONCESSIONS WITH REASONABLE OFFER!!!  Situated on oversized lot, NO HOA, almost 1 acre - only minutes from I-30, convenient to Historic downtown Royse City, schools, Rockwall, Greenville and Dallas on quiet cul de sac street in Royse City ISD. This home features formal dining, separate office with french doors plus a game room AKA bonus room upstairs for 2nd living! The open floor plan over looks the large fenced backyard with plenty of room for a POOL OR SHOP! Master features a separate shower, double vanities and 3rd custom master closet 12 x 13 - formerly a 4th bedroom, seller willing to convert back to a 4th bedroom with reasonable offer. Office has a closet - could be 5th bedroom! Spacious secondary bedrooms, fireplace in living room which is open to kitchen and dining.  Another BIG PLUS is the family safe room aka above ground tornado shelter located in the garage. Don't miss your opportunity in this highly sought after established neighborhood.
